Subject: [PATCH] block: allow gendisk's request_queue registration to be
Git-commit: fa70d2e2c4a0a54ced98260c6a176cc94c876d27
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
References: bsc#1104967,FATE#325924, bsc#1159142
